quran[99]{c,v,t}:
  15,1,"Alô. Wigi d issekniyen n Tezmamt, u d Leqwôan ipbegginen."
  15,2,"Ahat wid ijehlen ssaramen ad ilin d imvuâen."
  15,3,"Eoo iten ad ççen, ad zhun, a ten issedhu usirem. Deqqal ad éôen."
  15,4,"Ur Nesquccu tamdint, siwa ma d ayen i s iuran, ipwassnen."
  15,5,"Ur illi lois ara d isqeôben, ne$ ara iswexxôen lajel is."
  15,6,"Nnan: ""a win u$uô d irs usmekti! Keçç, war ccekk, d aôehbani."
  15,7,"Acimi ur a$ d tusiv ara, s lmalayek, ma d tidep ay tessawalev""?"
  15,8,"Ur Nesrusu lmalayek, siwa s tidep. Imiren, ur pganin."
  15,9,"Ih, Nekwni Nessers ed asmekti. Ih, Nekwni a Nêareb fellas."
  15,10,"Ni$ Nuzen ed, uqbel ik, i ikabaren imezwura."
  15,11,"Ur ten id ippas umazan, mebla ma ttahan fellas."
  15,12,"Akka ay t Nessekcam deg ulawen ibe$wviyen."
  15,13,"Ur uminen yis, ulamma ooan d imezwura tannumi."
  15,14,"Xas ad asen Nelli tabburt igenni, ad ppalin $uôes,"
  15,15,"a d inin, war ccekk: ""ittules iéôi nne$, ne$ nekwni d agdud iwumi sseêren""."
  15,16,"Ni$ Nerra itran deg igenni. Ncebbeê iten i wid ipmuqulen."
  15,17,"Nesdari ten, si yal cciîan imenfi."
  15,18,"Kkes ed win d issemêessen s tufra, A p iddu, fellas, ujajiê n ûûeê."
  15,19,"Tamurt Nessewsaâ p; Nerra fellas idurar; Nessem$i d, degs, yal cci, s lmizan."
  15,20,"Nerra, degs, lqut i kunwi, akw i wid ur tecceççayem ara."
  15,21,"Lexzayen n yal cci, $uône£ kan. Siwa s lkil ipwassnen i ten id Nesrusu."
  15,22,"Nuzen ed avu isswayen. Nesse$li d aman seg igenni, yissen Nessew ikwen. Ur llin ara lexzayen is $uôwen."
  15,23,"Ih, d Nekwni i Issidiren, i Ineqqen. D Nekwni ay d Iweôôaten."
  15,24,"Ni$ Nessen imezwura nnwen, Nessen ineggura."
  15,25,"Ih, Mass ik, Neppa, a ten id Ifser. Ih, Neppa, d Bab n ûûwab, d Amusnaw."
  15,26,"Ni$ Nexleq amdan si talaxt taberkant i meslen."
  15,27,"Nexleq loenn, iu$ lêal, si tmes n ccili."
  15,28,"Mi Inna Mass ik, i lmalayek: ""Nek Xelqe$ amdan, si talaxt taberkant i meslen."
  15,29,"Mi t Mesle$, u Üûuve$ as si ôôuê iW, ersemt $uôes, knumt""."
  15,30,"Knant akw lmalayek, akken ma llant,"
  15,31,"siwa Iblis, iugi ad yili ar wid iknan."
  15,32,"Inna: ""a yIblis, acu ik iu$en, ur telliv ar wid iknan""?"
  15,33,"Inna: ""ur kennu$ i umdan, i Txelqev si talaxt taberkant i meslen""."
  15,34,"Inna: ""effe$ segs! Aql ak, ihi, d imenfi."
  15,35,"Ih, fellak ddell alamma d ass uqeîîi""."
  15,36,"Inna: ""a Mass iw! Eoo iyi alamma d ass n tnekra nnsen""."
  15,37,"Inna: ""ih, keçç seg wid ipganin,"
  15,38,"ar ass n yiùmir ipwassnen""."
  15,39,"Inna: ""a Mass iw! Imi yi Terriv d a$ewway, war ccekk, ad asen cebbêe$ ddunit, a ten $ewwu$, akken ma llan."
  15,40,"Kkes ed imdanen iK izedganen garasen""."
  15,41,"Inna: ""$uôI, wagi d abrid uwqim."
  15,42,"War ccekk, ur tesâiv adabu $ef imdanen iW, siwa wid i k ivefôen seg imjaêen""."
  15,43,"Loahennama, s tidep, d ppaâud nnsen akw."
  15,44,"D m ûa tebbura; ar yal tabburt, s urbaâ ines."
  15,45,"Ih, wid ipêezziben, di leonanat akked tliwa:"
  15,46,"kecmet pen di tifrat, akked laman""!"
  15,47,"Nekkes i illan d dd$el, deg idmaren nnsen. D atmaten, deg imîeôêen, mqabalen."
  15,48,"Ur âaggun degsen, ur ten id ssuffu$en segsen."
  15,49,"Xebbeô ixdimen iW; Nek, s tidep, Psemmiêe$, Pêunu$."
  15,50,"U aâaqeb iW d aâaqeb aqeôêan."
  15,51,"Xebbeô iten $ef inebgawen n Ibôahim."
  15,52,"Mi kecmen $uôes, nnan: ""tifrat""! Inna: ""s tidep, nugad ikwen""."
  15,53,"Nnan: ""ur ppagwad, a k nbecceô kan, s uqcic amusnaw""."
  15,54,"Inna: ""tbecceôm iyi d, mi wessre$. Acu iyi d tbeccôem""?"
  15,55,"Nnan: ""Nbecceô ik id, s tidep, ur ppili seg wid iuysen""."
  15,56,"Inna: ""anwa iuysen aêunu n Mass is, siwa im$eôôqen""?"
  15,57,"Inna: ""d acu ay d lmeqsud nnwen, a yimceggâen""?"
  15,58,"Nnan: ""Nekwni, s tidep, neppuceggaâ d s agdud ibe$wviyen."
  15,59,"Kkes ed tawacult n Luî, ara nsellek akw,"
  15,60,"siwa tameîîut is. Ih, Nseyya a ppili, neppat, seg ineggura""."
  15,61,"Mi ôuêen imceggâen ar twacult n Luî,"
  15,62,"inna: ""kunwi, s tidep, d imdanen ur nessin""."
  15,63,"Nnan: ""xaîi, Nusa d, $uôek, s wayen rran di ccekk."
  15,64,"Nusa d, $uôek, s tidep. Nekwni, war ccekk, nessawal tidep."
  15,65,"Öuê akked twacult ik, mi mazal yiv. Ddu deffir sen. Ur d itezzi yiwen degwen! Âaddit anda i wen ippunefk lameô""."
  15,66,"Nseyya yas lameô agi: a d gwrin ad pwagezmen wakali."
  15,67,"Usan d, imezda$ n temdint, feôêen."
  15,68,"Inna: ""wigi, s tidep, d inebgawen iw, ur iyi cmmatet."
  15,69,"Ëezbet i Öebbi, ur iyi sdullut""!"
  15,70,"Nnan: ""day ur ak negdil ara imdanen""?"
  15,71,"Inna: ""atent an issi, ma taânam""."
  15,72,"S tudert ik, ar ddebdeben si ssekôan nnsen!"
  15,73,"Iwwet iten usu$u, tafrara."
  15,74,"Nesrewt ip. Nesse$li d fellasen ageffur n yiéôa n talaxt."
  15,75,"Deg waya, s tidep, d issekniyen i wid issnen ad ssikden."
  15,76,"Apan, ih, deg ubrid n yal ass."
  15,77,"Deg waya, s tidep, d assekni i lmumnin."
  15,78,"Ih, llan At Teégi, war ccekk, d imednas."
  15,79,"Nerra d ppaô segsen. Ihi, atent an, snat nni, deg ubrid ibanen."
  15,80,"Ni$ At Lêioô skaddben imazanen."
  15,81,"Nebbwi yasen d issekniyen nne£. Wexxôen asen."
  15,82,"Llan qqazen ixxamen n laman, deg idurar."
  15,83,"Iwwet iten usu$u, taûebêit."
  15,84,"Ulay sen ixdem wayen la keppben."
  15,85,"Ur Nexliq tamurt, igenwan, akked wayen illan garasen, siwa s tidep. Imir a d ias, war ccekk. Ihi, ssuref s lekyasa."
  15,86,"Ih, Mass ik d Axellaq, d Amusnaw."
  15,87,"Ni$ Nefka yak d ûa i usniles, akked Leqwôan ameqwôaêan."
  15,88,"Ur pmuqul ar wayen is N$at kra n twaculin nnsen. Ur $webbel ilmend nnsen. Zger tacvaî ik $ef lmumnin."
  15,89,"Ini: ""nekkini, s tidep, d aneddaô ipbegginen."
  15,90,"Akken id Nessers i wid ibvan,"
  15,91,"i irran Leqwôan d iêricen."
  15,92,"S Mass ik, ard a ten Nesteqsi akw"
  15,93,"$ef wayen xeddmen!"
  15,94,"Ihi, emdeê ayen i$ef i k ippunefk lameô, îixxeô i imcurak."
  15,95,"Ih, a k Nqennaâ mgal wid ittihin,"
  15,96,"i irran ôebbi nniven, ar tama n Öebbi. Deqqal ad éôen."
  15,97,"Ni$ Neéôa ar ul ik, keçç, iaâûeô seg wayen qqaôen."
  15,98,"Sbuccaâ Mass ik s ccekôan. Ili seg wid ikennun."
  15,99,"Aâbed Mass ik, ar k id ias utebbet!"
